http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/Arsonists%E2%80%99-target/article13982380.ece

Some miscreants burnt the car of Denkada mandal praja parishad president Kandi Chandrasekhar on Sunday night. According to information received here, the car that was parked in front of his house at Akkivaram in Denkada mandal was completely burnt even before eyewitnesses alerted the MPP about the incident.Following a complaint lodged by Mr. Chandrasekhar, Vizianagaram ASP A.V. Ramana, CLUES and dog squad visited the village.This was for the second time within eight months that his parked car was burnt by unidentified persons.